-05-13')\n\n# decay rate: semi-major axis decay is negative; report positive decay magnitude? question says decay rate (km/day). We'll return average rate (km/day) of change (likely negative), but ordered pair expects decay so use negative->abs.\nquiet_decay = -quiet_rate\nstorm_decay = -storm_rate\n\nprint('quiet_n', qn, 'quiet_rate_km_day', quiet_rate, 'quiet_decay', quiet_decay)\nprint('storm_n', sn, 'storm_rate_km_day', storm_rate, 'storm_decay', storm_decay)\n\n# round to 3 decimals for stability\nprint(round(quiet_decay,6), round(storm_decay,6))\n"}) [toolUseId=call_DfJiLT1jJJNrKuJ9anHdOeoW]
